1
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:22,680
County Deputy.

2
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,600
You are caught in the illusion of Crimson Greed Lycoris.

3
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,520
You will be trapped in your own greed

4
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:36,320
for the rest of your lives.

5
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,040
Hahaha.

6
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:53,040
Why does this tree look so familiar?

7
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,360
Greetings, Grandmaster.

8
00:03:02,800 --> 00:03:04,000
Grandmaster?

9
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,720
Me?

10
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,440
Grandmaster.

11
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:12,680
The demons of the Kui Clan in the West Mountain have been wiped out.

12
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,120
The remaining Flood Dragons of the Rakshasa Sea

13
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,450
are still making moves.

14
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,540
Should we eradicate them as well?

15
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,600
Eradicate them.

16
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:23,600
The Flood Dragons have been there for a millennium. They are quite powerful.

17
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,560
I wish to take a hundred thousand golden-body disciples

18
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,240
under your command to go.

19
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,680
Please grant your permission.

20
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:30,340
How many? A hundred thousand?

21
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,280
Do you think it's not enough?

22
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,360
Then a million.

23
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,040
Oh, no.

24
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:36,090
A hundred thousand is fine. Go.

25
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,280
Grandmaster.

26
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,650
These are the supreme spells we seized

27
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,520
while encircling the Kui Clan.

28
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,450
Please accept this, Grandmaster.

29
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,160
Advanced magic.

30
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:53,920
Good.

31
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,040
Hahaha.

32
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:08,400
Hahaha, hahaha.

33
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,480
Gesang.

34
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,120
Gesang.

35
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,840
Why,

36
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,720
Gesang,

37
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:07,080
don't you want to cultivate with me?

38
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,640
Of course I do.

39
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,520
Illusion.

40
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,760
I wanted to spare your lives.

41
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,320
Since you are government officials,

42
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,760
I didn't want to kill you myself.

43
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,320
However,

44
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:49,840
since you dared to bring someone to fight me,

45
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:55,040
don't blame me for not giving you a chance.

46
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:56,000
Witch!

47
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,400
Kill us if you want.

48
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,600
We failed the people of Er City

49
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,040
by believing your nonsense.

50
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,440
We may not be able to catch you today,

51
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,760
but someone will avenge us.

52
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,840
Fine.

53
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,440
Let's see

54
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,400
who else can save you today.

55
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,560
Break!

56
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:30,800
What? How could the illusion of Chilan Bi'an

57
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,400
be broken?

58
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,600
Could it be...

59
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,000
you have no greed?

60
00:07:08,360 --> 00:07:09,920
Golden blade shines, breaking through all.

61
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,180
Embrace the origin, shake the universe.

62
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,800
An immortal!

63
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,040
So this is

64
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:39,740
the Sanshan Sect's

65
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,360
Golden Immortal.

66
00:07:42,400 --> 00:07:43,159
You,

67
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:46,320
are actually the Liujin Immortal of the Three Mountains!

68
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:46,850
[Search]

69
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:16,360
Please.

70
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:44,020
The betrothal gift is meager, but I hope you will accept it.

71
00:08:46,960 --> 00:08:48,640
I only have this one daughter,

72
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,920
and I worry about having no one to manage the bank.

73
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,250
If you want to marry her,

74
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:55,490
you must marry into our family.

75
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:13,490
I will leave the Rui family's business to you.

76
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:14,930
I will work hard.

77
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:18,360
Keep up the good work.

78
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,280
Mr. Wang,

79
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:24,440
we'll really need your help with the bank matter this time.

80
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,480
This business yields a full 20 percent profit.

81
00:09:29,520 --> 00:09:30,440
Look,

82
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:33,200
we must settle the accounts clearly with them.

83
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,440
What are you all good for?

84
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,040
Regarding this debt,

85
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,240
if I can't collect it,

86
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:41,130
how will I answer to my father-in-law?

87
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,520
Open it.

88
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,520
Open it!

89
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:01,960
Take it.

90
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:02,960
Here, take it.

91
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,360
You're finally here, sir.

92
00:10:19,680 --> 00:10:20,760
Sir.

93
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,520
Drink this cup.

94
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,560
Come on.

95
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:41,720
Father.

96
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,880
Father.

97
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,400
Don't scare me.

98
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,480
Father.

99
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:48,760
Father.

100
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,640
Father.

101
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,280
Don't leave me.

102
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,520
Come.

103
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:36,080
Yichen.

104
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,160
Yichen.

105
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,080
What are you doing?

106
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,320
The Way of Heaven is constant.

107
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:24,120
Everything has a fixed destiny.

108
00:14:24,160 --> 00:14:25,620
Let go of anger and hatred.

109
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,320
Return to the right path.

110
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,640
It is not too late.

111
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:35,520
Ping Jieqiang Haihui.

112
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:35,680
Jieqiang Hai.
